Notes: WU ranked No. 1 in WBCA Coaches Poll. WU goes on 17-4 run to turn a 1-point
UMR lead into a 35-23 halftime lead. Brooke Ubelaker leads WU with season-high
17 pts and 10 rbs -- her 5th career double-double. WU shoots 58 percent in the
2nd half (17 of 30) -- next game vs NWMSU on Wednesday in Lee Arena.
Game.Officials: Phil Griffin,  Richard Brewer and Bart Tyson
